Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.24,0:00:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Riki's just a few inches away from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.08,0:00:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I hope this dream never ends.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.20,0:01:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,1000)}Wafu!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.58,0:01:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Kud, calm down! It's me!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.05,0:01:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why are Riki and I sleeping in the same bed?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.24,0:01:31.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Please be gentle with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.42,0:01:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Come again?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.12,0:01:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The girlfriend in me is super happy that you'd \Nrisk yourself sneaking into the girls' dorm for me,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.88,0:01:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,but this is all just moving so fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.64,0:01:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on! Y-You don't remember anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.88,0:01:43.14,Alt,,0,0,0,,Wafu!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.94,0:01:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Have we crossed that line already?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.72,0:01:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not what I meant.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.52,0:01:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You really don't remember \Nwhy I stayed the night?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.40,0:01:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Wafu?
Comment: 0,0:01:59.70,0:02:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.64,0:02:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, a home run!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.38,0:02:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,That puts us five points ahead! \NVictory's in the bag now!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.42,0:02:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,The ball has gone quite far.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.81,0:02:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice home run there, Masato!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.76,0:02:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,See that, Riki?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.26,0:02:14.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Those are the muscles of a mega slugger!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.74,0:02:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Muscles, yay yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.38,0:02:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Muscles, muscles!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.22,0:02:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Muscles, yay yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.92,0:02:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{Hmm? }Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.95,0:02:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.66,0:02:25.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What the heck?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.78,0:02:31.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It would seem the boys' dorm has been flooded \Nby a pipe burst from a runaway baseball.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.33,0:02:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn the luck! \NWho would do such a thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.42,0:02:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It was you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.42,0:02:38.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.00,0:02:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You've gotta be kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.46,0:02:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are we gonna sleep now?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.60,0:02:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Kanata{-san}, what will the boys do \Nduring summer vacation?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.30,0:02:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It's true it wouldn't be fair to ask them \Nto sleep in the classrooms or the gym.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.62,0:02:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,The boys will have to stay \Nin the empty rooms in the girls' dorm.
Comment: 0,0:02:57.11,0:02:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Ohhhh!
Comment: 0,0:02:58.07,0:02:59.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Ehhhh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.32,0:03:02.99,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll assign the rooms by lottery.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.41,0:03:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.64,0:03:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,No. 4! Who's got No. 4?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.00,0:03:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It's gotta be Riki, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.50,0:03:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.60,0:03:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Why does my lot say "Rin"?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.06,0:03:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the seed, Kyousuke{Natsume-kun}.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.92,0:03:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It wouldn't be bad to spend some family time \Nwith your sister during the break, now would it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.32,0:03:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. Fine by me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.10,0:03:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't wanna!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.10,0:03:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what does "better luck next time" mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.02,0:03:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Riki{Naoe-kun}, you drew that one, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.20,0:03:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't actually have enough \Nrooms open in the girls' dorm.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.80,0:03:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,There you have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.88,0:03:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll be staying in the home economics clubroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.08,0:03:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Riki!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.24,0:04:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you really going to stay in the clubroom?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.84,0:04:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I drew the bad lot, \Nso it seems that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.38,0:04:14.81,Default,,0,0,0,,U-Um, actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.56,0:04:18.62,Default,,0,0,0,,The thing is...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.58,0:04:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm still...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.90,0:04:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,looking for a roommate.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.20,0:04:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,So, that's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.98,0:04:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you like to be my roommate?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.14,0:04:42.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, but a girl and boy \Nstaying in the same room—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.74,0:04:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,If siblings can do it, \NI don't see why a couple can't, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.70,0:04:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I think I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.38,0:04:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Riki is so rational.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.16,0:04:57.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.34,0:05:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,That was actually just an excuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.38,0:05:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I really just want to spend \Nmore time with you, is all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.54,0:05:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I just being greedy?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.16,0:05:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's how the two of us \Nended up staying in your room.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.16,0:05:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-That rings a bell.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.54,0:05:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Though I'm not sure how \Nwe ended up in the same bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.50,0:05:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Kudryavka, what was that \Nscream just now about?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.60,0:05:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,K-K-Kanata{-san}!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.24,0:05:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Open up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.13,0:05:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm changing, so give me a second, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.68,0:05:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Kudryavka, why are you answering \Nthe door like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.88,0:05:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd feel bad to keep you waiting.
Comment: 0,0:05:43.15,0:05:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Eek!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.24,0:05:47.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'm trying to change!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.57,0:05:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you please come back later?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.58,0:05:54.45,Default,,0,0,0,,There are guys staying in the dorms now, \Nso think about the way you dress.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.45,0:05:56.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's a guy in this room right now, \Nnot just the dorms!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.87,0:05:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I-It's okay! Riki isn't in the room right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.98,0:06:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course he isn't. \NWhere did that come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.60,0:06:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,And what if he were here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.98,0:06:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,All the guys staying in the girls' dorm would \Nbe held at fault and forced to leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.10,0:06:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,They'd have to sleep in the classrooms \Nfor the summer instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.93,0:06:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would you ask something \Nlike that, Kudryavka?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.94,0:06:25.07,Default,,0,0,0,,B-Because Riki isn't in here right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.94,0:06:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, of course he isn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.12,0:06:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Now hurry up and get changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.22,0:06:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't bring much.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.34,0:06:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It's summer, so I don't have to \Nworry about bulky clothes.{*}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.74,0:06:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Where should I put my underwear?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.96,0:06:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You can put them in the top drawe—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.78,0:07:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait up, Riki!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.35,0:07:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Wafu!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.54,0:07:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't look!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.07,0:07:05.16,Alt,,0,0,0,,I'm not looking!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.16,0:07:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm totally not thinking "Huh, they're pretty small" \Nor "You've got some sexy stuff in here."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.30,0:07:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Kudryavka{-kun}, may I have a moment?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.78,0:07:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuiko{Kurugaya-san}!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.00,0:07:23.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.18,0:07:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there something you need?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.42,0:07:30.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep. I'm here to return the panties I borrowed \Nwhen I visited the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.80,0:07:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,When did you borrow those?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.12,0:07:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuiko{Kurugaya-san}, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.48,0:07:40.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm putting them back where I got them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.96,0:08:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{Hmm, i}It's summer all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.38,0:08:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Wafu?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.98,0:08:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,That didn't stay a secret long.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.82,0:08:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'm sure Yuiko{Kurugaya-san} will keep it to herself!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.47,0:08:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Ku{-chan}, I'm coming in!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.38,0:08:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Komari{-san}, what's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.52,0:08:29.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, when I came to hang out the other day—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.06,0:08:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. I guess it's summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.38,0:08:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Komari{Kamikita-san} found out, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.00,0:08:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine! I'm sure it's all going to be okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.12,0:08:57.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It sure is summer, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.26,0:08:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Kud, let's go get breakfast!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.94,0:09:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds good! There's nothing to hide \Nif we're out in public!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.66,0:09:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,My my, summer's in the air.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.44,0:09:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like the cat's out of the bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.96,0:09:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Wafu.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.66,0:09:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Riki!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.06,0:09:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you been lonely?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.44,0:09:23.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you miss my muscles?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.45,0:09:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Easy, Masato!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.22,0:09:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Riki, you can come stay in our room.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.38,0:09:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll have our muscles sandwich{futon} \Nlaid out and ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.28,0:09:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,With Kengo on the bottom, me on top, \Nand you right in the middle!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.18,0:09:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, tell me more.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.58,0:09:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I can tell you're worried about \Nyour childhood friend,
Comment: 0,0:09:37.44,0:09:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.32,0:09:42.06,Default,,0,0,0,,but it's senseless of you to make \Nlight of his determination.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.06,0:09:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.96,0:09:44.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, more so than anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.18,0:09:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It's summer, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.90,0:09:49.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup, yup. It's summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.31,0:09:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Totally summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.40,0:09:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.30,0:09:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It's senseless because it's summer?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.10,0:09:59.41,Default,,0,0,0,,That seems to be the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.78,0:10:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Pokey.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.44,0:10:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up, oaf.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.92,0:10:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Haruka{Saigusa-san}, is that a new joke item of yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.28,0:10:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I made a static generator \Nfor my research project!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.78,0:10:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. So it's a toy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.28,0:10:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It's {\i1}science{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.18,0:10:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, we've got our research \Nprojects to think about.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.46,0:10:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you going to do, Masato?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.44,0:10:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,A growth record of my muscles, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.66,0:10:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't make it sound like you're logging \Nthe growth of morning glories.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.22,0:10:41.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What about you, Kud?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.82,0:10:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I know exactly what I'm doing!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.29,0:10:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a rocket, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.04,0:10:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.58,0:10:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryachka, been doing well?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.60,0:11:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Long time no see, Yuki{Himuro-san}!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.62,0:11:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,She's visiting from our sister school \Nfor her research this summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.30,0:11:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Yuki Himuro, \Npresident of science club over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.70,0:11:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You know her?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.14,0:11:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, she was my roommate \Nwhen I was in Tevua.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.32,0:11:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,That's quite the interesting \Nproject you're working on.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.88,0:11:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I think so, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.56,0:11:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to do my summer \Nproject on water rockets!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.12,0:11:44.68,Default,,0,0,0,,All done!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.68,0:11:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you make this yourself, Ku{-chan}?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.02,0:11:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.86,0:11:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the first time I've made one,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.72,0:11:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,so there's probably lots of room \Nfor improvement.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.38,0:11:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,That's amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.16,0:11:57.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Now we just need \Nto use this to pump in air.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.06,0:12:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Couldn't we just use a compressor?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.70,0:12:07.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It's getting harder and harder.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.22,0:12:10.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like doing isometrics.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.66,0:12:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much, Masato{Inohara-san}!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.48,0:12:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like it's ready for takeoff.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.66,0:12:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Cleared for launch!{*}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.78,0:12:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Starting countdown!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.22,0:12:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,T-minus!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.74,0:12:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,5!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.68,0:12:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,4!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.64,0:12:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,3!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.68,0:12:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,2!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.68,0:12:30.39,Default,,0,0,0,,1!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.39,0:12:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Ignition!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.28,0:12:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,That was amazing, Kud!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.90,0:12:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It flew that far with just water and air!
Comment: 0,0:12:48.02,0:12:49.78,Alt,,0,0,0,,Yep, yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.60,0:12:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,That was only a prototype.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.74,0:12:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to record data and keep \Nexperimenting to make it go farther.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.78,0:13:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,My advice is to start with the wings' shape.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.58,0:13:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,,If you shape them like propellers,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.36,0:13:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,you can make the rocket spin, \Nwhich will stabilize its trajectory.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.89,0:13:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,A rocket launching into the blue summer sky, \Nsoaring among white clouds.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.82,0:13:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,That's youth.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.20,0:13:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's all launch our own water rockets.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.02,0:13:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,The one who emerges victorious in the end
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.56,0:13:24.15,Default,,0,0,0,,will be given the title "Rocket King"!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.82,0:13:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Mission start!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.14,0:13:35.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Rock, paper, scissors!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.79,0:13:37.37,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.90,0:13:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.83,0:13:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so good at this, Haru{-chan}!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.58,0:13:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Rin{-chan}, do your best!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.30,0:13:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, it's hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.44,0:13:52.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop complaining and get a move on.
Comment: 0,0:13:53.42,0:13:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Comment: 0,0:13:53.93,0:13:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Waaah!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.90,0:13:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,My rockets!
Comment: 0,0:13:59.77,0:14:00.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah...
Comment: 0,0:14:03.36,0:14:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yoh! Hah! Yah!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.06,0:14:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Wafu!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.64,0:14:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,This will keep you from dropping them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.34,0:14:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.04,0:14:24.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I heard you say \Nsomething about rockets.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.02,0:14:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you making water rockets with those?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.10,0:14:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,How'd you know, miss?{Do you know about rockets, miss? -a}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.42,0:14:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, we're actually going to \Nmake rockets ourselves!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.12,0:14:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,All of you? Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.23,0:14:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You must be super good friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.30,0:14:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have friends like that,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.48,0:14:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,so I have to make them by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.40,0:14:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is Kudryavka Noumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.92,0:14:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you tell me your name?{a tad bit more formal maybe}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.30,0:15:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Shiina Arizuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.71,0:15:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, Shiina{-san}, we're friends now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.88,0:15:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,No pressure or anything, but would you \Nlike to make water rockets with us?{I love the first part, nice}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.22,0:15:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.58,0:15:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.46,0:15:27.86,Default,,0,0,0,,They're welcome cookies for you and Yuki{Himuro-san}!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.86,0:15:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,These are for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.36,0:15:31.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I could drink this many in my sleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.61,0:15:33.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all soda, though?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.94,0:15:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Kengo, let's see which of us \Ncan down more of these!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.72,0:15:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Seems it's time for me \Nto put you in your place.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.26,0:15:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,,My eyes! My eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.12,0:15:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You brought that on yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.66,0:16:01.02,Default,,0,0,0,,This is fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.20,0:16:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Now then, let's all make rockets \Nout of the empty bottles!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.60,0:16:26.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Would shaping carbon nanotube \Nlike a bottle be cheating?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.40,0:16:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,That's against the rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.12,0:16:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Carbon nanotube?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.42,0:16:34.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It's what's used to make real rockets.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.18,0:16:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Real rockets?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.44,0:16:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.54,0:16:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Shiina{-san}, what made you \Nwant to make a water rocket?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.98,0:16:44.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to become an astronaut!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.31,0:16:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Wafu!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.72,0:16:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,My dream's to become a kosmonavt, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.76,0:16:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,My mother is even a kosmonavt.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.50,0:16:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,She's in{on?} the International Space Station right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.26,0:17:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Kud{-san}?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.20,0:17:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.50,0:17:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's get back to work!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.80,0:17:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, who's going to launch theirs first?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.13,0:17:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.40,0:17:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,This rocket was jointly \Ndeveloped by Anego{*} and me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.16,0:17:21.89,Default,,0,0,0,,The Sexy Anego{*}!{don't forget to make it sound like a space ship haha -a}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.77,0:17:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It's her picture on the rocket,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.42,0:17:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,but Komari{Kamikita-san} doesn't have \Nany part in it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.54,0:17:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep, yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.64,0:17:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It's one of my most prized photos.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.68,0:17:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll reveal Komari{-kun} in quite \Nthe steamy position post launch.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.00,0:17:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?! When did you take that picture?!
Comment: 0,0:17:38.87,0:17:40.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Huu! Huu!
Comment: 0,0:17:40.99,0:17:41.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1440,1024)}Masato!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.99,0:17:42.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1440,1024)}Masato!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.74,0:17:42.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(480,1024)}Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.49,0:17:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Ignition!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.12,0:17:44.58,Alt,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.74,0:17:52.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Drat. You can't see Komari{-kun} in all her \Nshame with how far it's flown.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.14,0:17:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't look at it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.51,0:17:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Strelka, don't fetch it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.24,0:17:59.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, next up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.14,0:18:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, here's the Naoe, made by Komari{-san} and me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.88,0:18:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Why me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.22,0:18:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Masato{Inohara-san}, if you would, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.00,0:18:09.18,Default,,0,0,0,,On it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.32,0:18:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Once it is launched, the photos of Riki{-san} and Kyousuke{-san} \Nwill turn into ones where they're hugging each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.78,0:18:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.78,0:18:15.92,Alt,,0,0,0,,Wafu?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.92,0:18:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I shopped it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.68,0:18:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Ignition.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.96,0:18:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Belka, wait up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.04,0:18:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It went farther than the Saigusa-Kurugaya team's.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.94,0:18:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like we're up next.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.04,0:18:33.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.22,0:18:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Chest!{NN: Do you have any idea why he'd be yelling this? Is it a kendo term or something being misheard by the TL or just something random being screamed? I can hear different things depending what I'm listening for.}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.22,0:18:37.84,Alt,,0,0,0,,Fungaaaargh!{*}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.30,0:18:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to launch them with water and air,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.56,0:18:45.94,Default,,0,0,0,,so that's against the rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.94,0:18:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.94,0:18:47.02,Alt,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.36,0:18:48.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You idiots.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.05,0:18:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.56,0:18:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Hoozawhat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.92,0:18:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,We really have to use just water and air?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.40,0:19:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,All right! Next up, it's Riki, \NNoumi, and Shiina.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.66,0:19:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(323,1024)}Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.66,0:19:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(941,1024)}All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.66,0:19:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1555,1024)}Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.96,0:19:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Kud{-san}, can I become an astronaut?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.92,0:19:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Becoming a kosmonavt is a big dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.42,0:19:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,But as long as you don't give up, \Nyou'll get there for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.40,0:19:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You really think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.20,0:19:39.69,Default,,0,0,0,,No doubt about it.{Yup, that's what I firmly believe. -a}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.94,0:19:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As long as you don't give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.26,0:19:48.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Kud, we're good to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.88,0:19:50.79,Default,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.56,0:19:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Ready for takeoff!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.14,0:19:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Countdown!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.56,0:19:56.21,Default,,0,0,0,,5!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.54,0:19:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,4!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.48,0:19:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,3!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.48,0:19:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,2!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.46,0:20:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,1!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.40,0:20:02.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Ignition!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.94,0:21:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,My mom's way of finding \NPolaris is a bit strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.12,0:21:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,She'd start from the Summer Triangle.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.60,0:21:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,If you put Altair of Aquila on the other side of the line \Nconnecting Vega of Lyra and Deneb of Cygnus,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.26,0:21:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,that's where you'll find Polaris.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.26,0:22:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Is something the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.52,0:22:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been looking at me for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.04,0:22:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just thinking about \Nhow much you love your mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.86,0:22:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.22,0:22:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Riki, could you listen to me for a bit?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.66,0:22:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.{more like a confused noise rather than a confirmation. figure it out during qc i guess}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.36,0:22:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,My mom is a really amazing person.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.84,0:22:36.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I admired her, and she was my goal.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.02,0:22:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My mom has been a kosmonavt \Nfor as long as I can remember,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.98,0:22:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and she has always cheerfully told me \Nthe importance of space exploration.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.66,0:22:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The reason I wanted to go to space...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.16,0:23:00.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\fad(0,478)}The reason I wanted to become a kosmonavt was because I wanted to see the same things my mom did.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.14,0:23:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wanted to find out that the things she said \Nshe enjoyed are actually fun myself.{*}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.76,0:23:10.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That was my dream.{That's why I choose this to be my dream  -a}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.24,0:23:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But that was a really difficult road to follow.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.84,0:23:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The further I went, the further away \Nit felt like my mom was.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.06,0:23:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Before I knew it, \NI had stopped in my tracks.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.54,0:23:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I ran away from my mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.16,0:23:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I didn't have the confidence to live up \Nto her expectations and ran away from Tevua.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.62,0:23:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It was just that, a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.18,0:23:53.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to keep at it and become a kosmonavt, \Nthinking that would somehow justify it.{*}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.92,0:24:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I think being able to talk to someone about your \Ndreams is pretty impressive on its own.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.08,0:24:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Riki.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.16,0:24:08.17,Default,,0,0,0,,That makes me want to keep \Ncheering you on by your side.{*}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.16,0:24:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you. Really.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.74,0:24:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,So, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.52,0:24:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it okay if I cast a good-luck charm?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.12,0:24:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,A charm?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.66,0:24:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a charm for tying people who \Ntreasure each other together.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.98,0:24:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,We draw our coat of arms on each other, \Nand they turn into stronger bonds and oaths.{*}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.71,0:24:48.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Kud?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.17,0:24:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-This is very embarrassing, \Nwhile also very important and serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.38,0:25:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you marry me?{*}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.23,0:25:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,M-Ma-Marry?! Like tying the knot?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.40,0:25:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,We're still in school, so I'm not trying \Nto get ahead of myself or anything,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.00,0:25:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,,but I've got about that level \Nof serious commitment.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.06,0:25:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, I got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.12,0:25:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's do it.
Comment: 0,0:25:32.00,0:25:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Mnh.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.40,0:25:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Wafu!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.24,0:25:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Please keep still.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.26,0:25:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.04,0:25:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,My coat of arms is filled with \Ncurvy waves and mountains.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.58,0:25:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,My mom told me they were gears.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.84,0:25:52.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Gears?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.16,0:25:56.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to be a good set of gears to you.
Comment: 0,0:26:01.86,0:26:02.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.12,0:26:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Wafu.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.20,0:26:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Kud, keep still.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.38,0:26:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm very sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.20,0:26:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.28,0:26:18.89,Default,,0,0,0,,This is embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.20,0:26:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It tickles.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.94,0:26:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of pattern \Nare you drawing on me?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.12,0:26:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Trees, I guess?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.38,0:26:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,They'll always be there around you, \Nprotecting you from whatever comes.{NN: Commented out is my take at trying to adapt how it's supposed to represent his name. If you feel it's unimportant, we don't have to do anything with it.}
Comment: 0,0:26:31.38,0:26:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,From the "Ki" in my name, like me,
Comment: 0,0:26:33.32,0:26:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,they'll always be there around you, \Nprotecting you from whatever comes.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.68,0:26:52.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Riki.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.70,0:27:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing I can't do \Nas long as Riki's with me.{removed italics}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.08,0:27:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My place is by Riki's side.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.16,0:27:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No matter where that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.94,0:27:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kud, wake up.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.96,0:27:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Wafu?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.16,0:27:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Kud.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.50,0:27:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Even in your dream, \Nyou're there right next to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.12,0:29:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Riki's just a few inches away from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.04,0:29:46.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&HFFFFFF&\t(1992,3994,\c&H000000&)}I hope this dream never ends.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.64,0:29:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Morning, Kud.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.04,0:30:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning, Riki.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.96,0:30:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It's pretty quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.72,0:30:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened to everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.56,0:30:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, right. They all went home.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.34,0:30:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,All summer long,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.58,0:30:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Riki and I have been alone together.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.16,0:30:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Riki, let's go get breakfast!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.49,0:30:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, the cafeteria staff aren't here.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.08,0:30:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't I make \Nbreakfast for you, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.68,0:30:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You would do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.58,0:30:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course! \NI'd be happy to!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.46,0:30:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll come get you once I'm done, \Nso just hang around in my room until then.
Comment: 0,0:31:18.64,0:31:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Wafu.{yeah this ain't a wafu}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.50,0:31:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm making miso soup for Riki.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.50,0:31:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like we're newlyweds!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.14,0:31:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you just going to \Nkeep running away?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.72,0:31:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuki{Himuro-san}, you're a strong person,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.12,0:31:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,so there's no way you'll \Nunderstand how I feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.30,0:31:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm trying to be strong, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.28,0:32:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I just come off as strong \Nto you as a result.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.90,0:32:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the only reason I can stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.60,0:32:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You've noticed, haven't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.82,0:32:11.32,Default,,0,0,0,,That this place is closed off.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.44,0:32:19.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You going to keep repeating this?{*}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.52,0:32:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Kyousuke{-san} said something similar.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.96,0:32:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,And now, Yuki{Himuro-san}, you're \Ntelling me the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.20,0:32:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It just means you want someone to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.22,0:32:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as Riki's with me, \NI don't need anything else!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.40,0:32:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all I need!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.42,0:32:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As long as Riki's with me...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.36,0:32:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As long as he's there...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.64,0:32:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Riki, breakfast's ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.68,0:32:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Riki?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.94,0:33:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Riki! Riki!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.42,0:33:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Riki?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.42,0:33:07.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Riki!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.59,0:33:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Riki!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.00,0:33:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Riki!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.52,0:33:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.88,0:33:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I've always known.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.92,0:33:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a world tailored perfectly to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.68,0:33:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,A misguided paradise that I created.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.56,0:33:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to become stronger, \Neven if just within this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.54,0:33:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,If I could get just a little better. \NBecome just a bit stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.94,0:34:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps I could take flight one day, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.60,0:34:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No. That's no more than a pipe dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.12,0:34:12.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll never be more than I am.
Comment: 0,0:34:13.12,0:34:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Kud!{original timing}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.12,0:34:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Kud!{including the echo}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.50,0:34:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Riki?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.18,0:34:21.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Kud!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.49,0:34:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm coming for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.04,0:34:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Riki? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.48,0:34:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll get these chains off right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.52,0:34:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Riki! Please stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.98,0:34:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.06,0:34:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I remember everything. \NI know what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.36,0:35:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I've already given up because of \Nthe accident on the field trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.86,0:35:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a relief to have it all come to \Nan end without me running away.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.00,0:35:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,But I wanted you, \Nmy dearest Riki, to be saved,{*}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.38,0:35:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,so I prayed over and over.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.88,0:35:29.31,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why, just knowing you got out fine \Nwas more than enough for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.27,0:35:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not enough for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.78,0:35:35.18,Default,,0,0,0,,We were going to rescue everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.66,0:35:40.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Kud, I wanted to become someone strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.30,0:35:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to understand \Nwhat it meant to be strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.70,0:35:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted the strength to protect somebody.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.16,0:35:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And I learned. Learned from all of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.04,0:35:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I learned what it meant from you!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.46,0:36:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I was able to wake up.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.32,0:36:08.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.46,0:36:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I relived all of this over and over.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.84,0:36:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I kept reliving it all over and over and over \Nbecause it was just so much easier,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.60,0:36:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,and I kept running away from reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.88,0:36:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'll do it again. I'll relive it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.52,0:36:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm weak. I'll never \Nbreak free of these chains.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.04,0:36:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll only ever be the earthbound Kudryavka.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.90,0:36:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not true at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.46,0:36:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been looking for a way \Nto get stronger this whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.46,0:36:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Riki.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.40,0:36:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got this. \NYou already know what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.66,0:36:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.50,0:36:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Kud!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.41,0:37:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Riki, where are we going?!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.56,0:37:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want it bad enough, \Nthere's nowhere you can't fly!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.28,0:37:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Your heart will set you free!{*}{NN: I know this isn't quite what it's saying, but god that whole "feelings reaching" spiel is awful.}{*}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.14,0:37:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Ku{-chan}, I've filled it up with water!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.38,0:37:24.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Komari{-san}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.32,0:37:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all set and ready to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.86,0:37:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Mio{Nishizono-san}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.54,0:37:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You can count on our \Ncalculations for the wings!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.70,0:37:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The wind's calm. \NIt's the perfect time for launch.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.32,0:37:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Haruka{Saigusa-san}! Yuiko{Kurugaya-san}!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.38,0:37:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Masato{Inohara-san}! Kengo{Miyazawa-san}!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.50,0:37:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,We're leaving the rest to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.76,0:37:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Just ten more pumps!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.76,0:37:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Noumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.98,0:37:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's a new mission for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.82,0:37:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Surpass yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.12,0:37:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Kud, give it all you've got!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.40,0:37:55.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.72,0:37:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Kyousuke{-san}.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.92,0:37:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Rin{-san}.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.94,0:38:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, Kud!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.02,0:38:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The mission's started!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.42,0:38:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.94,0:38:10.22,Default,,0,0,0,,10... 9...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.06,0:38:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,8... 7...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.20,0:38:17.27,Default,,0,0,0,,6...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.08,0:38:22.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been running away this whole time. \NCan you really get any stronger?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.80,0:38:26.65,Default,,0,0,0,,5!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.16,0:38:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,All you've been doing is reliving \Nthis sunny world of yours.{*}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.16,0:38:34.37,Default,,0,0,0,,4!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.94,0:38:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You, the Kudryavka who's bound \Nby chains and cannot fly.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.58,0:38:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to get stronger! \NI want to fly!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.48,0:38:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're going to do it, \Nstick it out to the very end.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.12,0:38:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't just have all the fun yourself. \NLet me join in, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.10,0:38:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryachka, believe in yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.86,0:38:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuki{Himuro-san}.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.04,0:39:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuki{Himuro-san}!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.56,0:39:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as you don't give up, \Nyour wish will come true for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.34,0:39:08.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.18,0:39:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,3...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.50,0:39:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,2...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.64,0:39:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,1...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.60,0:39:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Kud, hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.90,0:39:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,1...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.80,0:39:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Kud?!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.34,0:39:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Kud!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.02,0:39:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&\t(833,1333,\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&)}Kunya.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.46,0:40:13.43,Default,,0,0,0,,1...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.76,0:40:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Kud!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.47,0:40:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.22,0:40:19.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Riki?!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.89,0:40:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Riki, wait up!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.85,0:40:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't get stronger by myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.64,0:40:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't fly if you aren't there next to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.70,0:40:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Riki!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.32,0:40:38.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kud.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.45,0:40:39.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Kud!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.41,0:40:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Kud!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.02,0:40:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Riki?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.90,0:40:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Is Riki on the other side of the sky?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.06,0:40:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Has he been watching \Nover me this whole time?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.74,0:41:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. Riki and I are connected.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.90,0:41:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Riki. I'm on my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.22,0:41:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Ready for takeoff!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.36,0:41:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Starting countdown!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.74,0:41:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,T-minus.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.38,0:41:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}9, 8, 7, 6, 5, 4, 3!{added 4 and 3 and extended timing}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.66,0:41:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Those chains represent my weakness.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.68,0:41:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The weakness of seeking strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:29.04,0:41:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They may appear to be connections, but they're actually rejections.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.76,0:41:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I have friends who are there for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.38,0:41:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Whenever I'm feeling lonely or in trouble, \Nthey're always there for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.76,0:41:46.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And Riki has always been there \Nto support me as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.56,0:41:48.62,Default,,0,0,0,,2! 1!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.82,0:41:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Ignition!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.60,0:42:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Riki?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.90,0:42:25.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Riki.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:25.43,0:42:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Kud!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:25.98,0:42:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Did Ku{-chan} wake up?!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.40,0:42:27.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Little Kud!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.86,0:42:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you feeling okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.16,0:42:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Kudryavka{-kun}!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:30.36,0:42:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Kud{Noumi-san}.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.02,0:42:31.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.78,0:42:32.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Noumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:43.14,0:42:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Morning, Kud.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.06,0:43:00.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:00.35,0:43:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Ku{-chan}!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:00.35,0:43:01.26,Alt,,0,0,0,,Kud!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.26,0:43:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurray! Hurray!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:05.04,0:43:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}After that long, long dream, \NI finally managed to wake up.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.68,0:43:17.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wanted to save Riki, \Nbut he saved me in the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:29.41,0:43:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I never knew about this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:31.76,0:43:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew I wanted to come here \Nwith you as soon as I found it.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:37.20,0:43:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You can see all kinds of stars \Nhere when it gets dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:41.38,0:43:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,If it sounds good to you, \Nwould you like to come stargazing some time?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.64,0:43:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'd love to.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:48.74,0:43:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Riki, would you mind \Nhearing me out on two things?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:52.62,0:43:53.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Two things?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:54.82,0:43:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The first is a question I have.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:58.00,0:44:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think strength actually is?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:03.34,0:44:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I think you've already found \Nthat answer yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:07.14,0:44:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't quite understand it yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:10.40,0:44:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think you're strong \Njust because you're not weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:15.54,0:44:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it's just understanding \Nwhat it means to be weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:19.78,0:44:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Wafu?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:21.17,0:44:26.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the ability to acknowledge you are weak \Nand take even just one step forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:26.02,0:44:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I think it means to be strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:30.72,0:44:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:32.60,0:44:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,How philosophical.
Comment: 0,0:44:34.76,0:44:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Hehe.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:36.44,0:44:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the other thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:41.04,0:44:43.57,Default,,0,0,0,,The second thing is something \NI wanted to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:45.76,0:44:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to work hard \Nto become a kosmonavt.
