Dialogue: 0,0:44:57.92,0:45:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,but I still want to work towards it.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:00.78,0:45:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,So you've set your mind to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:02.44,0:45:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:05.06,0:45:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,U-Um... {aatowa - O-One more thing... -Hybrid}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:07.64,0:45:12.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it okay if I add just one more thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:19.88,0:45:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Riki.
